libsoftware-copyright-perl (0.004-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.
  * Move Dist::Zilla plugins from Build-Depends-Indep to Build-Depends
    and remove their '<!nocheck>'annotations.
    `dh clean' calls `dzil clean' which fails if the plugins are not
    available.
    Also move libmodule-build-perl which is used by `dzil build'.

 -- gregor herrmann <gregoa@debian.org>  Sun, 02 Oct 2022 13:52:41 +0200

